# Internal/operator Meta-Layer project data — regenerated fresh from Drive (META_DATA_ROOT) at
# build time by scripts/build-card-data.js. Repo is public: a git-tracked copy is fetchable via
# raw.githubusercontent.com regardless of the deploy-time public trim (scripts/deploy-public-trim.mjs),
# so these must never be committed. card-data.json / cards-*.json are the intentionally-public
# partner-facing outputs and are NOT listed here — those stay tracked.
/public/registry.json
/public/operator-*.json
/public/sorular-*.json
/public/strateji-*.json
